  "text": "Together with the results shown in Figure 1 , the data above can be used to estimate the approximate percentage of transfected cells that are Hcrt neurons. Because we counted on average 1161 hM3Dq-transfected neurons in each tissue series, we can expect to find ϳ7000 transfected cells in each Gad2-IRES-Cre;R26R-EYFP mouse. Because AAV expression occurred in ϳ14% of Hcrt cells and, assuming there are ϳ 4000 Hcrt neurons in a mouse [CITATION_1] , we estimate that ϳ560 Hcrt neurons were transfected in each mouse which corresponds to Ͻ8% of the total number of transfected neurons.",
